      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELECTRIC ASSENT (4) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from five starts. Was out of the placings last time (18.62) at Richmond in a NG, finishing sixth and beaten 8 lengths. Rates on top and should go close. MY MOON SHADOW (1) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at The Gardens over 400m (22.88). Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Can do much better this time. NOVA LASS (6) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 22.50 beating Jet Fuel. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Sure to be thereabouts. MISS MAXI (3) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish.",
